       java.util.Date parsedDate = dateFormatLocal.parse(date);

Use &lt;code&gt;dateFormat.format&lt;/code&gt; for taking input Date (which is always UTC), timezone and return date as String. 

How to store UTC/GMT time in DB:&lt;BR&gt;
----------------------------------- 
