The reason why you get the output you are getting now is that sorting happens [alphanumerically][3]

Here a is a very basic way of doing it. This code uses simple `String`-operation to extract the numbers. This works if you know the format of the filename, in your case `Spectrum_&lt;number&gt;.txt`. A better way of doing the extraction is to use [regular expression][4].

	public class FileNameNumericSort {
	
